creator: QSuper
descriptionHtml:
If you're a QSuper member, the QSuper app makes it easy for you keep your super on track. You can:

• Log in securely via username and password
• Get convenient access to your account using a PIN
• View your balances and investment breakdown
• Access our investment performance
• Provide your employer with the information they need to contribute
• Access your BPAY details to make contributions
• Check your profile information is up to date
• Find our contact details and location

Download the app to get started. You'll need your Member Online username and password to access the app for the first time. You can register for online access or reset a forgotten password on our website at https://qsuper.qld.gov.au

If you're not yet a member, join online in minutes and become part of an award-winning profit-for-members fund with over 100 years experience managing Australian superannuation.

We're always improving the services we offer our members. Please contact us with any feedback, suggestions or questions by writing a review or emailing us directly at qsuper@qsuper.qld.gov.au.
descriptionShort: Staying on top of your super just got a whole lot easier.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We've added the ability to view performance information within the app.
